val dataTempTemp = sqlContext.read
.format("com.databricks.spark.csv")
.option("header", "true") // Use first line of all files as header
.option("inferSchema", "true") // Automatically infer data types
.option("delimiter", ",")
.load("/data/sidana/purch/experiments/atleast_one/inputData").withColumn("utcdate",unix_timestamp($"utcdate","yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss").cast("timestamp"))
val dataTemp = dataTempTemp.filter(to_date(dataTempTemp("utcDate"))>="2017-02-04"&&to_date(dataTempTemp("utcDate"))<="2017-03-05")
val interactions = dataTemp.groupBy(dayofyear(dataTemp("utcDate"))).count.withColumnRenamed("dayofyear(utcDate)","day").sort("day")
interactions.rdd.coalesce(1,false).saveAsTextFile("/data/sidana/purch/experiments/atleast_one/online_setting/stats/interactionsTemp")

val usersTemp = dataTemp.select(dayofyear(dataTemp("utcDate")),dataTemp("userId")).distinct.withColumnRenamed("dayofyear(utcDate)","day").sort("day")
val users = usersTemp.groupBy("day").count
users.rdd.coalesce(1,false).saveAsTextFile("/data/sidana/purch/experiments/atleast_one/online_setting/stats/usersTemp")
